data.name: New Pokédex
rules: Shuffle your deck. Then, look at up to 5 cards from the top of your deck and rearrange them as you like.

effect.name: Vine Pull
effect.text: Once during your turn when Dark Ivysaur retreats, choose 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon and switch it with his or her Active Pokémon.

attacks.name: Fury Strikes
attacks.text: Your opponent puts 3 markers onto his or her Pokémon (divided as he or she chooses). (More than 1 marker can be put on the same Pokémon.) Then, this attack does 10 damage to each Pokémon for each marker on it. Don't apply Weakness and Resistance. Remove the markers at the end of the turn.

attacks.name: Swift Lunge

attacks.name: Stir Up Twister
attacks.text: Your opponent switches the Defending Pokémon with 1 of his or her Benched Pokémon. Then, switch your Active Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon. (Do the damage before switching the Pokémon.)

attacks.name: Mass Explosion
attacks.text: Does 20 damage times the total number of Koffings, Weezings, and Dark Weezings in play (Apply Weakness and Resistance.). Then, this attack does 20 damage to each Koffing, Weezing, and Dark Weezing (even your own). Don't apply Weakness and Resistance.

attacks.name: Stun Gas

attacks.name: Horrid Pollen
